text: Hive is a 2021 Kosovan Swiss Albanian Macedonian drama movie directed by first time director Blerta Basholli and starring Yllka Gashi, Çun Lajçi, Aurita Agushi, Kumrije Hoxha, Adriana Matoshi, Molikë Maxhuni, Blerta Ismaili. It was released on November 5, 2021 in the United States. == Other websites == * Category:2021 drama movies Category:Kosovan movies Category:Swiss drama movies Category:Albanian movies Category:Macedonian movies
